citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:40 AM on 19 Oct
2022. Inspectors spoke with the licensee who indicated that no one was available to perform an inspection due to being
several hours away.
End Section
